data.description: Beautifully updated home in Hyrum and walking distance to the reservoir! This 2 bd 1 bth home has been fully updated and has another room in the basement that can be finished for a 3rd bedroom. Water heater, A/C, shower, and laminate has all been updated in the last year. Three fruit trees were just planted 3 months ago in the backyard and the shed is included and can be used as a chicken coop like it is now or converted back to a shop. Assumable VA Loan of 5.875% rate to veterans only.
